WEBVTT

00:02:58.637 --> 00:03:01.869
discovering they have access to superpower,

00:03:01.869 --> 00:03:04.496
one that requires the skill and tenacity

00:03:04.496 --> 00:03:06.004
of their intellect,

00:03:06.004 --> 00:03:09.565
but thankfully no radioactive spiders.

00:03:09.565 --> 00:03:11.406
But with great power

00:03:11.406 --> 00:03:13.710
comes great responsibility,

00:03:13.710 --> 00:03:17.374
and you all like to think that if we had such powers,

00:03:17.374 --> 00:03:19.653
we would only use them for good.

00:03:19.653 --> 00:03:23.000
But what if you could read your ex's emails,

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:26.112
or add a couple zeros to your bank account.

00:03:26.112 --> 00:03:28.132
What would you do then?

